      <title>以色列以罢工结束加沙停战，将哈马斯归咎于崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/israel-say-it-s-launching-strikes-on-hamas-targets-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在加沙横跨加沙的一夜之间发动了空袭，哈马斯说，数百人杀死了数百人，与巴勒斯坦集团打破了将近两个月的停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/israel-say-it-s-launching-strikes-on-hamas-targets-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 00:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
